  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>An <em>olivine pendeloque aeon stone</em> imparts the calmness of still earth and a solidity of thought, granting you a +2 item bonus to saving throws against effects that cause the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied} conditions.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate—Still Earth</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">R</span> (concentrate)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You become confused, frightened, or stupefied</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The stone suppresses the triggering effect for 1 minute, but the calming urges impose a –1 status penalty to your attack rolls.</p>"
